tomer prior to the current booking.\n","\n","19. **previous_bookings_not_canceled:** Number of previous bookings that were not canceled by the customer prior to the current booking.\n","\n","20. **reserved_room_type:** Code of the room type reserved by the customer (e.g., A, B, C, etc.).\n","\n","21. **assigned_room_type:** Code for the type of room assigned to the customer (e.g., A, B, C, etc.).\n","\n","22. **booking_changes:** Number of changes made to the booking from the moment it was made until the arrival.\n","\n","23. **deposit_type:** Type of deposit paid:\n","\n",">No Deposit\n","\n",">Non Refund\n","\n",">Refundable\n","\n","24. **agent:** ID of the travel agent who made the booking (if applicable).\n","\n","25. **company:** ID of the company/entity that made the booking (if applicable).\n","\n","26. **days_in_waiting_list:** Number of days the booking was in the waiting list before confirmation.\n","\n","27. **customer_type:** Type of customer, such as:\n","\n",">Transient: A regular guest booking individually.\n","\n",">Contract: A booking under a contractual agreement.\n","\n",">Group: A booking for a group of customers.\n","\n",">Transient-party: A transient booking that is part of a group.\n","\n","28. **adr:** Average Daily Rate, defined as the total revenue per available room. It's calculated by dividing the sum of all lodging transactions by the number of occupied lodging nights.\n","\n","29. **required_car_parking_spaces:** Number of car parking spaces required by the customer.\n","\n","30. **total_of_special_requests:** Total number of special requests made by the customer (e.g., high floor, king bed, etc.).\n","\n","31. **reservation_status:** The current status of the reservation:\n","\n",">Canceled: Booking was canceled by the customer.\n","\n",">Check-Out: Customer has checked out.\n","\n",">No-Show: Customer did not show up.\n","\n","32. **reservation_status_date:** Date when the last reservation status was set."],"metadata":{"id":"yGJWaiysEeUf"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["# Variables Description of Objective types\n","df.describe(include=object).T"],"metadata":{"id":"M8jNsMIPBGvw"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["# Variables Description of int types\n","df.describe().T"],"metadata":{"id":"-VCuMs4BVtUF"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["# Check Unique Values for each variable.\n","\n","# Get the number of unique values for each column\n","unique_counts = df.nunique()\n","print(unique_counts)\n"],"metadata":{"id":"sUYlbaMkWFLM"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["## ***3. Data Wrangling***"],"metadata":{"id":"w-S8nnbraIya"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["### Data Cleaning"],"metadata":{"id":"6rjxyXPwag0k"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["#### Null Value Removing"],"metadata":{"id":"BFcQeoMQa3hQ"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["#To Find Null value\n","df.isnull().sum()"],"metadata":{"id":"egkBxzH3alYo"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["# Fill with mode Vlaue of column cuntry\n","mode_value_country = df['country'].mode()[0]\n","df['country'].fillna(mode_value_country,inplace = True)\n","\n","# FIll The mean value of column children\n","mode_value_children = df['children'].mean()\n","df['children'].fillna(mode_value_children,inplace=True)\n","\n","# Fill with the value of \"No Agent\" in column agent\n","df['agent'].fillna('No Agent', inplace = True)\n","\n","# Convert the column to object type to store string data\n","df['agent'] = df['agent'].astype('object')"],"metadata":{"id":"UJV6fuxvlp3t"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["# Drope the columan company\n","df.drop('company', axis=1, inplace=True)"],"metadata":{"id":"QNZo-LuSp42m"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["# Final out put after cleaning all null value\n","df.isnull().sum()"],"metadata":{"id":"AKcPoW2IatbF"},"execution_cou